    "body": "Django is one of the most powerful web frameworks for building modern web applications. \r\nIt allows developers to move quickly from an idea to a working application with minimal hassle. \r\n\r\nOne of its strongest features is the \"batteries-included\" philosophy, which provides tools for \r\nauthentication, ORM, admin interface, and more right out of the box. This makes it a great choice \r\nfor both beginners and experienced developers. \r\n\r\nWith Django, you can create secure, scalable, and maintainable projects while writing clean and \r\nreadable code. If you are starting your web development journey, Django is definitely worth exploring.",
    "publish": "2025-09-09T14:36:06Z",
    "created": "2025-09-09T14:40:57.050Z",
    "updated": "2025-11-29T09:57:17.743Z",
    "status": "PB"
  }
